com.amazon.device.associates
Class SearchByIdResponse

java.lang.Object
  com.amazon.device.associates.ShoppingServiceResponse
      com.amazon.device.associates.SearchByIdResponse

public class SearchByIdResponse
extends ShoppingServiceResponse

SearchByIdResponse is returned in the ShoppingListener.onSearchByIdResponse(SearchByIdResponse) callback. It returns the result of the product lookup initiated via ShoppingService.searchById(SearchByIdRequest). Product information can be retrieved using the getProducts() method. Product information is localized and includes product ID, product title, product description, product price, and product image URL.

Check getUnavailableProductIds() to get a list of products that are either invalid or unavailable.
